    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained over the years. The exterior is clean and well-kept, though it shows some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scratch on the rear passenger door consistent with regular use. Inside, the leather seats are well-preserved with only light wear on the driver's side bolster. All electronics and features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. The engine runs smoothly with no known mechanical issues, and the service history is up to date. It is a solid, dependable car that offers a great driving experience for its next owner.",
