    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3 in concours condition. This specimen features the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, delivering 414 hp with a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline facilitated by eight individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the original carbon fiber roof panel is perfectly preserved. Finished in Alpine White over Novillo",
